---
title: Szechuan-Inspired Pork and Green Bean Stir-Fry with Sesame-Cilantro Rice
description: Put down the takeout menu and make this easy, saucy Szechuan-inspired pork and green bean stir-fry. Savoury ground pork, green beans and sweet bell peppers make the perfect trio nestled atop steaming black sesame-studded cilantro rice.
